[src:rosetta-code/100-doors-p05] Fōrmulæ programs are not textual, visualization/edition of programs is done showing/manipulating structures but not text.
[src:rosetta-code/100-doors-p05] Moreover, there can be multiple visual representations of the same program.
[src:rosetta-code/100-doors-p05] Even though it is possible to have textual representation —i.e.
[src:rosetta-code/100-doors-p05] XML, JSON— they are intended for storage and transfer purposes more than visualization and edition.
