[src:rosetta-code/dining-philosophers-p05] A Rust implementation of a solution for the Dining Philosophers Problem.
[src:rosetta-code/dining-philosophers-p05] We prevent a deadlock by using Dijkstra's solution of making a single diner "left-handed." That is, all diners except one pick up the chopstick "to their left" and then the chopstick "to their right." The remaining diner performs this in reverse.
